721
00:33:53,769 --> 00:33:55,608
Lima lawan lima, pilih lima orang dulu.

722
00:33:55,889 --> 00:33:57,049
Abang Dai dan saya pasti tiada masalah.

723
00:33:57,328 --> 00:33:58,529
Termasuk Kak Qing juga.

724
00:33:58,769 --> 00:33:59,289
Siapa lagi?

725
00:33:59,488 --> 00:33:59,968
Tang San.

726
00:34:00,088 --> 00:34:00,488
Saya...

727
00:34:01,049 --> 00:34:02,129
Permintaan ini memang amat melampau.

728
00:34:02,848 --> 00:34:03,649
Tapi, saya benar-benar harap

729
00:34:04,049 --> 00:34:05,368
biar saya bertanding dalam pusingan ini.

730
00:34:05,608 --> 00:34:06,409
Tak boleh!

731
00:34:06,728 --> 00:34:08,049
Awak mampu lawan lima orang?

732
00:34:11,568 --> 00:34:13,328
Baik, serahkan pusingan ini kepada awak.

733
00:34:21,569 --> 00:34:22,849
Kita benar-benar tak bertanding?

734
00:34:24,329 --> 00:34:25,049
Percayai dia.

735
00:34:31,329 --> 00:34:32,609
Orang lain tak perlu berlawan.

736
00:34:33,208 --> 00:34:33,809
Dua lawan dua.

737
00:34:34,168 --> 00:34:35,128
Tentukan kemenangan dalam satu pusingan.

738
00:34:36,128 --> 00:34:37,249
Peraturan boleh diubah?

739
00:34:37,688 --> 00:34:39,009
Boleh, asalkan dua pasukan setuju.

740
00:34:39,329 --> 00:34:40,609
Tapi, dengan satu syarat.

741
00:34:41,569 --> 00:34:42,168
Apa syarat?

742
00:34:43,009 --> 00:34:43,928
Hidup atau mati diabaikan

743
00:34:45,769 --> 00:34:46,688
pada perlawanan.

744
00:34:49,408 --> 00:34:49,888
Baik.

745
00:34:51,049 --> 00:34:52,849
Kerajaan Xingluo boleh
mempunyai dua orang putera.

746
00:34:53,329 --> 00:34:54,049
Tapi, hanya seorang

747
00:34:54,289 --> 00:34:55,049
raja saja.

748
00:34:55,208 --> 00:34:56,049
Dengar, buat persiapan.

749
00:34:56,128 --> 00:34:57,089
Kita pergi selamatkan mereka

750
00:34:57,329 --> 00:34:58,249
kalau situasi tak terkawal.

751
00:34:58,488 --> 00:34:58,968
Baik.

752
00:34:59,769 --> 00:35:00,488
Boleh mula sekarang.

753
00:35:02,289 --> 00:35:03,128
Dua lawan dua.

754
00:35:03,569 --> 00:35:04,688
Kurang seorang lagi.

755
00:35:04,809 --> 00:35:06,009
Saya seorang dah cukup.

756
00:35:06,688 --> 00:35:08,769
Peraturan tak boleh diubah lagi.

757
00:35:09,128 --> 00:35:10,249
Dua orang diperlukan!

758
00:35:20,648 --> 00:35:21,688
Awak ikut serta supaya
bilangan orang kita mencukupi.

759
00:35:22,609 --> 00:35:23,249
Selepas mula,

760
00:35:23,968 --> 00:35:25,289
