761
00:35:25,888 --> 00:35:26,569
Mula sekarang!

762
00:35:40,609 --> 00:35:41,529
Apa teknik ini?

763
00:35:45,968 --> 00:35:47,049
Teknik gabungan Wuhun?

764
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:08,440
